rue,"entry_ids":["n1292","n1531"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AA%D9%8E%D8%A3%D9%8E%D9%88%D9%8E%D9%91%D9%87%D9%8E"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to moan, to groan"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of تَأَوَّهَ (taʔawwaha) (form V)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From the interjection آه (ʔāh)."},"ipa":["/ta.ʔaw.wa.ha/","/ta.ʔaw.wuh/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n1292","headword_ar":"تَاَوَّهَ","root":"An","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"; (M, K;) by reason of pain: (S, TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he complained"},{"kind":"text","text":"by reason of disease or pain: (TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he uttered a cry"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cries:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) said of a man. (S, Msb.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^an~iti Alqawosu","text_ar":"اَنِّتِ القَوْسُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tay^in~u","text_ar":"تَيِنُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aniynN","text_ar":"اَنِينٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The bow made a gentle and prolonged sound."},{"kind":"text","text":"(AHn, M.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA A^afoEaluhu maA A^an~a fiY Als~amaA='i najomN","text_ar":"لَا اَفْعَلُهُ مَا اَنَّ فِى السَّمَا=ءِ نَجْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I will not do it as long as there is a star in the heaven:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^an~a","text_ar":"اَنَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"being here a dial. var. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ean~a","text_ar":"عَنَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.) You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA A^an~a fiy AlfuraAti","text_ar":"مَا اَنَّ فِي الفُرَاتِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaTorapN","text_ar":"قَطْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"As long as there is a drop in the Euphrates."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA A^afoEaluhu maA A^an~a fiY Als~amaA='N","text_ar":"لَا اَفْعَلُهُ مَا اَنَّ فِى السَّمَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I will not do it as long as there is rain in the heaven"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.) [It is said in the M that Lh mentions the last two sayings; but it is there indicated that he read"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaTorapF","text_ar":"قَطْرَةً"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"samaA='F","text_ar":"سَمَا=ءً"},{"kind":"text","text":": and] ISk mentions the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA A^afoEaluhu maA A^an~a fiY Als~amaA='i najomFA","text_ar":"لَا اَفْعَلُهُ مَا اَنَّ فِى السَّمَا=ءِ نَجْمًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, M,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA Ean~a","text_ar":"مَا عَنَّ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY Als~amaA='i najomN","text_ar":"فِى السَّمَا=ءِ نَجْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (T;) [in the former of which,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^an~","text_ar":"اَنّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"must be a particle (which see below); but it seems that it should rather be"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~a","text_ar":"اـِنَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in this case, as ISd thinks; for he says,] I know not for what reason"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"An~","text_ar":"انّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is here with fet-h, unless a verb be understood before it, as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vabata","text_ar":"ثَبَتَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wujida","text_ar":"وُجِدَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": [and he adds,] Lh mentions"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA A^an~a *lika Aljabala makaAnahu","text_ar":"مَا اَنَّ ذلِكَ الجَبَلَ مَكَانَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as long as that mountain is in its place"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA A^an~a","text_ar":"مَا اَنَّ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiraA='F makaAnahu","text_ar":"حِرَا=ءً مَكَانَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as long as"},{"kind":"text","text":"Mount"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Hirà is in its place"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: but he does not explain these sayings. (M.)"}],"source_refs":["S","TA","Msb","M","K","T"]},{"entry_id":"n1531","headword_ar":"تاوّه","root":"Awh","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, Mgh, Msb, K;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^w~h","text_ar":"اوّه","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taA^owiypN","text_ar":"تَاْوِيةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, K;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A=ha","text_ar":"ا=هَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^awohN","text_ar":"اَوْهٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He said"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A=hi","text_ar":"ا=هِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^awohi","text_ar":"اَوْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c. [i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Ah!"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"alas!"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (S, Mgh, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he moaned;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"uttered a moan,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"moaning,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"prolonged voice of complaint;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tawaj~aEa","text_ar":"تَوَجَّعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","K"]}]}}